0A3B802">Speaker of the House of Delegates</span></p><p class="cs7A307AE2" style="tab-stops:left -62.75pt left -36pt left 0pt left 22.1pt left 36pt left 72pt left 98.6pt left 108pt left 144pt left 180pt left 216pt left 252pt left 288pt left 324pt left 360pt left 396pt left 432pt left 468pt left 504pt left 540pt left 576pt left 612pt left 648pt left 684pt left 720pt left 756pt left 792pt left 828pt left 864pt left 900pt left 936pt;"><span class="csE736517A">&nbsp;</span></p><p class="cs7A307AE2" style="tab-stops:left -62.75pt left -36pt left 0pt left 22.1pt left 36pt left 72pt left 98.6pt left 108pt left 144pt left 180pt left 216pt left 252pt left 288pt left 324pt left 360pt left 396pt left 432pt left 468pt left 504pt left 540pt left 576pt left 612pt left 648pt left 684pt left 720pt left 756pt left 792pt left 828pt left 864pt left 900pt left 936pt;"><span class="csE736517A">&nbsp;</span></p><p class="cs90E9E035" style="tab-stops:left -62.75pt left -36pt left 0pt left 22.1pt left 72pt left 98.6pt left 108pt left 144pt left 180pt left 216pt left 252pt left 288pt left 324pt left 360pt left 396pt left 432pt left 468pt left 504pt left 540pt left 576pt left 612pt left 648pt left 684pt left 720pt left 756pt left 792pt left 828pt left 864pt left 900pt left 936pt;"><span class="csE736517A">__________</span></p><p class="cs8DF0654B"><span class="csE736517A">&nbsp;</span></p><p class="cs8DF0654B"><span class="csE736517A">&nbsp;</span></p><p class="cs73AF651A"><span class="csE736517A">&nbsp;</span></p><p class="cs73AF651A" style="tab-stops:left 54pt;"><span class="csE736517A">	The within is ................................................ this the...........................................</span></p><p class="cs73AF651A" style="tab-stops:left 54pt;"><span class="csE736517A">&nbsp;</span></p><p class="cs73AF651A"><span class="csE736517A">Day of ..........................................................................................................., 2025.</span></p><p class="cs